{
  "texts": [
    "VOMS proxy certificate and JSON web tokens (JWTs) [40], to be used for authentication and authorization with computing resources.",
    "• Propagator periodically reports information on jobs and workers in Harvester to the PanDA server.",
    "• Job Fetcher prefetches the jobs from the PanDA server and stored them in the Harvester database.",
    "The jobs are later bound to workers and submitted.",
    "• Command Manager fetches commands from the PanDA server and stores them in the Harvester database."
  ]
}